ility to anticipate\nfuture demand and its transferability to cases unseen at the training stage.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 16 Oct 2022 23:30:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Apr 2023 20:23:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-14"}
