es. The proposed clutch\npresents great potential for developing safe, lightweight, and low-power\nphysical human-robot interaction systems, such as exoskeletons and robotic\nwalkers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 16 Oct 2022 23:53:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-18"}
