ments and simulations\nprovide valuable information about the atomic level stochastic and vibrational\ndynamics in Li2Si2O5 and their role in Li+ diffusion and vitrification.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2022 12:23:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-18"}
