ence of {\\kappa}_l. Our\nwork suggests that GeSe polymorphs with overall low thermal conductivity are\npromising contenders for thermoelectric and thermal management applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2022 03:02:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-19"}
